  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/101758967c96a5860a2b2848dfdf30e9.avif?t=1763835923\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/112b6c196a90ded5330a735f2f3ce63c.avif?t=1763835923\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a different and ingenious adventure in Mycelium Heaven where a fungus with a very peculiar diet will help save its home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your best strategy in this war and overcome levels where you'll discover new and complex mechanics that will test your logic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/5158ec5e5f8aa31e37c9a7d5fe913e18.avif?t=1763835923\" width=600 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive right in without complex tutorials and discover a fascinating world full of puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍄 Don't forget to use your wit and creativity to help the forest! 🍄</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/fe3ae13a72dd2ecfcf010ce256c1259c.poster.avif?t=1763835923\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/fe3ae13a72dd2ecfcf010ce256c1259c.webm?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/fe3ae13a72dd2ecfcf010ce256c1259c.mp4?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use mechanics where you use energy to: spread, bloom, or consume. The zombie apocalypse has already arrived!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍁 Interesting challenges will emerge from these rules! 🍁</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/a77cf9af1b138d2921df9ba6ea560a60.poster.avif?t=1763835923\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/a77cf9af1b138d2921df9ba6ea560a60.webm?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/a77cf9af1b138d2921df9ba6ea560a60.mp4?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover natural worlds set in different seasons of the year, where the environments will pose a real challenge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💀 Can you defeat all the zombies before it's too late? 💀</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/6a52d854dc3192d0afe0f85d10c02864.poster.avif?t=1763835923\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/6a52d854dc3192d0afe0f85d10c02864.webm?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/6a52d854dc3192d0afe0f85d10c02864.mp4?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/8ba1f618b8780c53bf5f04dec011cd1a.avif?t=1763835923\" width=600 height=303 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/101758967c96a5860a2b2848dfdf30e9.avif?t=1763835923\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/112b6c196a90ded5330a735f2f3ce63c.avif?t=1763835923\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a different and ingenious adventure in Mycelium Heaven where a fungus with a very peculiar diet will help save its home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your best strategy in this war and overcome levels where you'll discover new and complex mechanics that will test your logic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/5158ec5e5f8aa31e37c9a7d5fe913e18.avif?t=1763835923\" width=600 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive right in without complex tutorials and discover a fascinating world full of puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍄 Don't forget to use your wit and creativity to help the forest! 🍄</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/fe3ae13a72dd2ecfcf010ce256c1259c.poster.avif?t=1763835923\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/fe3ae13a72dd2ecfcf010ce256c1259c.webm?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/fe3ae13a72dd2ecfcf010ce256c1259c.mp4?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use mechanics where you use energy to: spread, bloom, or consume. The zombie apocalypse has already arrived!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🍁 Interesting challenges will emerge from these rules! 🍁</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/a77cf9af1b138d2921df9ba6ea560a60.poster.avif?t=1763835923\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/a77cf9af1b138d2921df9ba6ea560a60.webm?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/a77cf9af1b138d2921df9ba6ea560a60.mp4?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover natural worlds set in different seasons of the year, where the environments will pose a real challenge. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💀 Can you defeat all the zombies before it's too late? 💀</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/6a52d854dc3192d0afe0f85d10c02864.poster.avif?t=1763835923\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/6a52d854dc3192d0afe0f85d10c02864.webm?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/6a52d854dc3192d0afe0f85d10c02864.mp4?t=1763835923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656520/extras/8ba1f618b8780c53bf5f04dec011cd1a.avif?t=1763835923\" width=600 height=303 /></span></p>",
